:css
  body {
    font-family: Gotham, sans-serif;
  }

- code_org_link = link_to 'Code.org', 'http://code.org'

%p
  Hi
  = @enrollment.first_name + ','

%p
  Thank you for attending a Code.org
  = @workshop.course
  - if @workshop.course == Pd::Workshop::COURSE_CSF
    = @workshop.subject
  workshop on
  = @workshop.sessions.first.start_date_us_format + '.'

%p
  %strong
    Please tell us about your experience by filling out this 5 minute
    = link_to('survey', @survey_url) + '.'

%p
  %i Why? Because your opinion matters!!

%p
  Please note that the facilitator of your session and your Regional Partner will see your responses.
  Your name and email will not be shared with your facilitator or Regional Partner to protect your anonymity.
  However, it's possible your facilitator or Regional Partner could identify you from your written responses.

%p
  We are committed to continually improving our programs. We want our teachers to have the best workshops possible
  and your feedback helps us build the experience that teachers have in the future!

%p
  %a{href: @survey_url,
    style: 'width: 240px; height: 36px; border: 0; color: white; background-color: #FDC62C; font: bolder 18px Arial; display: block; text-align: center; line-height: 36px; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 5px;'}
    Take the 5 minute survey

- if @workshop.course == Pd::Workshop::COURSE_CSF && @workshop.subject == Pd::Workshop::SUBJECT_CSF_101

  %h3
    Get started with
    = @workshop.course

  %p
    To help you get started with
    = @workshop.course
    in your classroom, we've created these
    = link_to('Amazon lists', 'https://www.amazon.com/ideas/amzn1.account.AFRP6N2PQKQ73HHEN6SJNS5ONHEA') + '.'
    Also feel free to source similar items locally and use these lists as a checklist!

  %p
    If you have any questions, feel free to reach out to us at
    = link_to('teacher@code.org', 'mailto:teacher@code.org')
    or connect with other teachers on our
    = link_to('teacher forum', 'https://forum.code.org/') + '.'

- unless @workshop.subject == Pd::Workshop::SUBJECT_CSF_201
  %h3
    Additional workshop benefits

  - if @workshop.course == Pd::Workshop::COURSE_CSF
    %p
      There's a personalized certificate attached to this email acknowledging your successful completion of Code.org's
      = @workshop.course
      workshop.

  = render partial: 'iste'

  %p
    You've taken the first steps to making CS available to your students. We can't wait to see where you all go from here!
    Remember to keep us posted on Twitter @TeachCode.


- if @workshop.course == Pd::Workshop::COURSE_CSF
  %p
    Thank you,
    %br
    Megan Hochstatter
    %br
    K-5 Education Program Manager Code.org

- else
  %p
    Thank you,
    %br
    Baker Franke
    %br
    Research and Evaluation Manager
    = code_org_link

